issues.description: The template declares the existing Lecture fields (lectureName and numberOfInscribedStudents) as public, but the UML in the problem statement uses “–” (private) for all attributes and the reference solution makes them private. This visibility mismatch may confuse students about the correct access level for the attributes.
issues.suggested_fix: Change the template’s field declarations to private (e.g. private String lectureName; private int numberOfInscribedStudents; etc.) to match the UML and reference solution.
